productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Haiti and I bought one.
This parse works considerably well. It secretly improves my basketball by a lot.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
My co-worker Archer has one of these. He says it looks crooked.
